{"id":433,"category_slug":"english-conversations","category_name":"Conversations","position":35,"title":"35. Can I Drive There?","subtitle":"","level":"A1","parts":13,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/english-conversations/35-can-i-drive-there.433/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/35-can-i-drive-there-2022-03-07-21-16-17/0-35-can-i-drive-there.mp3","transcript":"What time is it?\nIt's three o'clock.\nOh no, I'm late.\nWhere are you going?\nTo the dentist.\nCan I drive you there?\nSure! That will help.\nDo you have a toothache?\nYes, and it's very bad.\nI'm sorry to hear that.\nI've had it for weeks, and this is the first time that I could get in.\nMy dentist is always so busy!\nI guess that's a good thing! It means a lot of people like him.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T20:48:40","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"What time is it?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/35-can-i-drive-there-2022-03-07-21-16-17/1.mp3","time_start":1.96,"time_end":2.9},{"position":2,"content":"It's three o'clock.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/35-can-i-drive-there-2022-03-07-21-16-17/2.mp3","time_start":2.9,"time_end":3.89},{"position":3,"content":"Oh no, I'm late.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/35-can-i-drive-there-2022-03-07-21-16-17/3.mp3","time_start":3.89,"time_end":5.22},{"position":4,"content":"Where are you going?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/35-can-i-drive-there-2022-03-07-21-16-17/4-2025-05-14-16-17-24.mp3","time_start":5.16,"time_end":6.04},{"position":5,"content":"To the dentist.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/35-can-i-drive-there-2022-03-07-21-16-17/5.mp3","time_start":6.04,"time_end":6.92},{"position":6,"content":"Can I drive you there?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/35-can-i-drive-there-2022-03-07-21-16-17/6.mp3","time_start":6.92,"time_end":7.98},{"position":7,"content":"Sure! That will help.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/35-can-i-drive-there-2022-03-07-21-16-17/7.mp3","time_start":7.98,"time_end":9.17},{"position":8,"content":"Do you have a toothache?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/35-can-i-drive-there-2022-03-07-21-16-17/8.mp3","time_start":9.17,"time_end":10.18},{"position":9,"content":"Yes, and it's very bad.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/35-can-i-drive-there-2022-03-07-21-16-17/9.mp3","time_start":10.18,"time_end":11.95},{"position":10,"content":"I'm sorry to hear that.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/35-can-i-drive-there-2022-03-07-21-16-17/10.mp3","time_start":11.95,"time_end":13.18},{"position":11,"content":"I've had it for weeks, and this is the first time that I could get in.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/35-can-i-drive-there-2022-03-07-21-16-17/11.mp3","time_start":13.19,"time_end":16.35},{"position":12,"content":"My dentist is always so busy!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/35-can-i-drive-there-2022-03-07-21-16-17/12.mp3","time_start":16.35,"time_end":18.65},{"position":13,"content":"I guess that's a good thing! It means a lot of people like him.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/35-can-i-drive-there-2022-03-07-21-16-17/13.mp3","time_start":18.74,"time_end":21.47}]}